# Skill Forge Display Font

Drop the official headline font here:

```
skill-forge-display.woff2   ← preferred
skill-forge-display.woff    ← fallback
skill-forge-display.otf     ← fallback
```

The branded theme loads this font for all `h1`–`h4` headings and cover titles. Characteristics from the brand kit:

- Italic sans-serif
- Bold / heavy weight
- Distressed or brushed texture (baked into the font file)

Until the font file is added, headings use **Arial Black / Impact** italic as a close fallback.
